name: Sydney & Sarah
description:
This is Sydney & Sarah (with an "h").
Sydney & Sarah are "friends."
Sydney & Sarah grew up together.
Now they are growing apart.
Sydney is secretly planning to move to L.A.
Sarah knows.
Sarah already misses Sydney.
